<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-93-0122 </DOCNO><TEXT>The short time available to attack ballistic missiles with a StrategicDefense Initiative (SDI) weapon system will preclude traditional national-leveldecision making. A unique command and control (C2) concept is requiredto best serve the balance between effectiveness and weapon system safety.This article develops that concept with a blend of autonomous operationwith man in the loop and advocates early resolution to ensure C2 strategyand tactics push technology development.</TEXT></DOC>